(4, 'Computer and IT Services', '<p>The IT Department&#39;s mission is is to ensure smooth functioning of day to day affairs of the Institute in an efficient and effective manner through building world-class competencies in the technical analysis, design, procurement, implementation, operation and support of computing infrastructure and services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The institute is equipped with the latest systems, a laser printer, Colored inkjet printers, scanners.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All the computers are connected through Local Area Network. We are having Windows 2016 server , a wire-based LAN Fibre Optics with NKN/NICNet connectivity of 1 GBPS bandwidth. We have around 65 nos. hardware including terminals employed. We are having Facility Management Contract between ICMR and HCL Infosystems Ltd. For the LAN.</p>\r\n', 'computer.jpg'),
(5, 'Animal House', '<h4>Animal Care Facility (ACF)</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>ACF building is located to small separate room On 13th Floor, in the institute , In the animal rooms are supplied with exhaust fan and air-conditioning, with sufficient lighting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The facility has been registered for breeding of and experiments on animals under the Committee for the Purpose of Control and Supervision of Experiments on Animals (CPCSEA), Ministry of Social Justice and Empowerment, Govt. of India. (Registration No. 25/124/2009-AWD by CPCSEA, New Delhi).</p>\r\n', 'rat.jpg');
