(7, 'Dr. Manisha Madkaikar', 'Pediatric Immunology & Leukocyte Biology', 'Director ', 'dr-manisha-1542685439-1.jpg', 'madkaikarmanisha@yahoo.co.in, directorniih@gmail.com ', '(+91-22) 2413 2928, ( +91-22) 2413 8518/19', '', '<ul class=\"style110\">\r\n	<li><strong>MBBS</strong> University of Mumbai ( Medicine; 1993)</li>\r\n	<li><strong>MD</strong> University of Mumbai (Residency in Internal Medicine &amp; its branches; 1997)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul class=\"style110\">\r\n	<li class=\"style109\">Member of European Society of Immunodeficiencies (ESID)</li>\r\n	<li class=\"style109\">Founder member of Indian Society for Primary Immune Deficiency (ISPID)</li>\r\n	<li class=\"style109\">Life member of The Cytometry Society (TCS)</li>\r\n	<li class=\"style109\">Life member of Indian Society of Haematology and Blood Transfusion</li>\r\n	<li class=\"style109\">Life member of Mumbai Haematology Society</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul class=\"style110\">\r\n	<li>Primary Immunodeficiency Disorders</li>\r\n	<li>Heamatological Malignancy</li>\r\n	<li>Marrow failure syndrome</li>\r\n	<li>Flow Cytometry</li>\r\n	<li>Molecular Biology</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul class=\"style110\">\r\n	<li>Dr. N.C. Kelkar award for standing first in M.D. (General Medicine) examination from Seth G.S. Medical College, Mumbai.</li>\r\n	<li>SSC Gold medal in Social Science</li>\r\n	<li>&lsquo;Associateship for specialized training of young scientists in niche areas of biotechnology&rsquo; awarded by department of biotechnology under which received training in Molecular Immunology at Institute of Child Health, London under Dr Gaspar. From March - Sept 2007.</li>\r\n	<li>Awarded 3rd prize for Poster &lsquo;Evaluation of expression of Bruton&rsquo;s Tyrosine Kinase in Monocytes from X- Linked Agammaglobulinemia by Flow Cytometric Analysis.&rsquo; Manisha Madkaikar, Kimberly Gilmour*, Bobby Gaspar* presented at 48th annual conference of Indian society of haematology and transfusion medicine held in Lucknow from 15th to 17th November 2007.</li>\r\n	<li>Best poster award for poster &lsquo;Overview of immunological profile of chronic lymphoproliferative disorders of patients referred to tertiary health care centre from western India.&rsquo; Presented at 49th annual conference of Indian society of haematology and transfusion medicine ISHTM 2008, Sept 19 - 21 2008, Pondicherry.</li>\r\n	<li>Best paper award for the paper &lsquo;Clinical spectrum of Leukocyte Adhesion Deficiency-I from India and antenatal diagnosis for LAD-I for the first time in India.&rsquo; Presented at Mumbai Haematology group annual conference held in 7th Nov 2009 at Tata Memorial Hospital, Mumbai.</li>\r\n	<li>Best oral paper award for &lsquo;Flowcytometric diagnosis of PNH&rsquo; at ISHTM held on 19 - 21st Nov 2010, Kolkata.</li>\r\n	<li>Best poster award for &lsquo;Application of flowcytometry for the diagnosis of Primary Immunodeficiency disorders&rsquo; presented at 3rd Annual Meeting of The Cytometry Society&rsquo;-India held on 19 - 20th Oct 2010 at NCBS, Bangalore.</li>\r\n	<li>Best oral paper award for &lsquo;Leukocyte Adhesion Deficiency I: To Delineate Molecular Defects in ITG&beta;2 gene and Utilize it in Prenatal Diagnosis&rsquo; 35th Annual conference of the Mumbai Hematology Group held on 3 - 4th march 2012.</li>\r\n	<li>Best poster award for poster on &lsquo;Diagnosis of Primary Immunodeficiency Disorders by flowcytometry&rsquo; 2nd International Conference on Primary Immunodeficiency Diseases&rsquo; held on 2 - 4th Feb 2013.</li>\r\n	<li>Awarded BGRC Oration by Mumbai Hematology Group during the annual conference held on 23rd - 24th march 2013 and oration delivered: &lsquo;Diagnosis of Primary Immunodeficiency Disorders: Our journey so far.&rsquo;</li>\r\n	<li>Dr Manisha Madkaikar was awarded &ldquo;Dr. Armida Fernandez Oration&rdquo;3ndAnnual CME of Dr. Athavale Foundation &amp; Pediatric Alumni LTMGH (DAFPAL) held on 5th October 2014, at Mumbai. She delivered an oration on &lsquo;PID: Navigating Through Uncharted Territory&rsquo;.</li>\r\n	<li>Received best paper award in clinical category for the year 2015, presented by The Cytometry Society, India. The paper entitled &lsquo;Differential antigen expression and aberrant signaling via PI3 / AKT, MAP / ERK, JAK / STAT and Wnt Beta catening in Lin- / CD38 - / CD34+ cells in AML was published in European Journal of Haemtology in April 2015.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h4>Ongoing Publications</h4>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Kerketta L, Rao VB, Madkaiker M, Ghosh K, Mohanty D, Jijina F. Biphenotypic expression in a case of acute leukemia with pericentric inv(6)(p12q24). Cancer Genet Cytogenet. 2005 Jun;159(2) : 187-9.</li>\r\n	<li>Manisha M, Ghosh K, Shetty S, Nair S, Khare A, Kulkarni B, Pathare AV, Baindur S, Mohanty D. Spectrum of inherited bleeding disorders from Western India. Haematologia (Budap). 2002;32(1) : 39-47.</li>\r\n	<li>Ghosh K, Jijina F, Shetty S, Madkaikar M, Mohanty D. First-time development of FVIII inhibitor in haemophilia patients during the postoperative period. Haemophilia. 2002 Nov;8(6) : 776-80. PMID : 12410646</li>\r\n	<li>Ghosh K, Madkaikar M, Jijina F, Gandhi S, Shetty S, Mohanty D. Open heart surgery with mitral valve replacement--ordeal of an undiagnosed haemophilia patient. Clin Lab Haematol. 2003 Apr;25(2) : 131-3. PMID : 12641618</li>\r\n	<li>Vundinti BR, Madkaikar M, Kerketta L, Jijina F, Ghosh K, Mohanty D, Jijina F. A novel translocation der(4)t(1;4)(q21;q35) and a marker chromosome in a case of myelodysplastic syndrome. Cancer Genet Cytogenet. 2003 Jul 15;144(2):175-6. PMID : 12850381</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h4>Completed Publication</h4>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Shetty S, Madkaikar M, Nair S, Pawar A, Baindur S, Pathare A, Ghosh K, Mohanty D. Combined factor V and VIII deficiency in Indian population. Haemophilia. 2000 Sep;6(5) : 504-7. PMID11012693</li>\r\n	<li>Ghosh K, Joshi SH, Shetty S, Pawar A, Chipkar S, Pujari V, Madkaikar M, Pathare AV, Jijina F, Mohanty Transfusion transmitted dis