(21, 'Dr. Swati Kulkarni', 'Transfusion Medicine', 'Scientist D', 'swati-kulkarni-1543487305-1.jpg', 'swatiskulkarni@gmail.com', '+( 91-22) 2413 8518/19', '', '<ul class=\"style110\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 35px 20px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; resize: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; resize: none; position: relative; list-style: none;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; resize: none; font-weight: 700;\">M.Sc.&nbsp;</span>University of Mumbai</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; resize: none; position: relative; list-style: none;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; resize: none; font-weight: 700;\">PhD&nbsp;</span>University of Mumbai</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul class=\"style110\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 35px 20px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; resize: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">\r\n	<li class=\"style109\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; resize: none; position: relative; list-style: none;\">Indian Society of Haematology and Blood Transfusion</li>\r\n	<li class=\"style109\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; resize: none; position: relative; list-style: none;\">Mumbai Haematology Group</li>\r\n	<li class=\"style109\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; resize: none; position: relative; list-style: none;\">Indian Women Scientist Association</li>\r\n	<li class=\"style109\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; resize: none; position: relative; list-style: none;\">Indian Society of Transfusion Medicine</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul class=\"style110\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 35px 20px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; resize: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; resize: none; position: relative; list-style: none;\">Immunohaematology</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; resize: none; position: relative; list-style: none;\">Transfusion Medicine</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; resize: none; position: relative; list-style: none;\">Molecular biology</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 17px; background: transparent; resize: none; font-family: inherit; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.1;\">Foreign Visits</h4>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; resize: none; line-height: 25px; text-align: justify;\">From 10 April to 10 August, 2016, visited Etablissement Fran&ccedil;ais du Sang &ndash; Bretagne, Inserm UMR1078, BREST, FRANCE as a part of CEFIPRA funded project &ldquo;Molecular study of RH gene variants in Indians&rdquo;s</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"style110\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 35px 20px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: rgb(246, 246, 246); resize: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: transparent; resize: none; text-align: justify; position: relative; list-style: none;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; resize: none;\">Patent: &quot;RHD gene allele associated with a weak D phenotype and its uses&quot;_ Patent was filed in Europe on March 8, 2017 under number 17 305246.5.</span>The inventors are Yann FICHOU (from EFS) and Swati KULKARNI (from Indian Council of Medical Research). The applicants are ETABLISSEMENT FRANCAIS DU SANG INSERM and NATIONAL INSTITUTE OF IMMUNOHAEMATOLOGY.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: transparent; resize: none; text-align: justify; position: relative; list-style: none;\">2012-2013&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; resize: none;\">ICMR international fellowship for Senior Scientist</span>, under Prof. Robert Flower, Research Programme Leader at Australian Red Cross Blood Service, Queensland, Australia trained for &ldquo;Non- invasive fetal RhD typing&rdquo;.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: transparent; resize: none; text-align: justify; position: relative; list-style: none;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; resize: none;\">&ldquo;Award of Excellence&rdquo;</span>&nbsp;for extraordinary contribution in the field of Transfusion Medicine by Indian Society of Blood Transfusion and Immunohaematology during 42nd Annual conference held at Kota from 8-10th Dec 2017.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: transparent; resize: none; text-align: justify; position: relative; list-style: none;\">&ldquo;A.J. Desai &amp; L.H Hiranandani best poster award at 38th Annual conference of Mumbai Haematology Group. 2015 for poster entitled &ldquo;Noninvasive fetal RhD typing&rdquo;.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: transparent; resize: none; text-align: justify; position: relative; list-style: none;\">Best poster award First prize at 4th Annual Conference of Indian Society of Transfusion Medicine 2015 held at Kolkata from 4th to 6th December, 2015 &ldquo;Frequency of clinically significant blood group antigens in Ahir community from Valsad (South Gujarat)&rdquo;</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: transparent; resize: none; text-align: justify; position: relative; list-style: none;\">Postgraduate Travel fellowship award from 4th annual conference of Indian Society of Blood Transfusion held at Delhi, Sept 2015 for oral presentation &ldquo;Noninvasive fetal RHD genotyping using cell-free fetal DNA from maternal plasma&rdquo;.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: transparent; resize: none; text-align: justify; position: relative; list-style: none;\">Best oral presentation award for &ldquo;Molecular genotyping of Human Neutrophil Antigen-3 among Indian blood donors&rdquo; at 5th Annual Conference of Indian Society of Transfusion Medicine, Transmedcon 2016 held at Bhopal.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: transparent; resize: none; text-align: justify; position: relative; list-style: none;\">Second prize for oral presentation &ldquo;A NOVEL FUT1 MISSENSE MUTATION IDENTIFIED IN AN INDIAN WITH PARA-BOMBAY PHENOTYPE&rdquo; at 41st Annual National conference of Indian Society of Blood Transfusion and Immunohaematology in Pune, sept 2016.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: transparent; resize: none; text-align: justify; position: relative; list-style: none;\">Best oral presentation award for &ldquo;Molecular genotyping of Human Neutrophil Antigen-3 among Indian blood donors&rdquo; at 5th Annual Conference of Indian Society of Transfusion Medicine, Transmedcon 2016 held at Bhopal.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: transparent; resize: none; text-align: justify; position: relative; list-style: none;\">Second prize for oral presentation &ldquo;Serological and molecular screening of RhD negative individuals for DEL phenotype&rdquo; at Diamond Jubilee International Conference of NIIH on &ldquo;Revolution of Laboratory Medicine In Modern Biology&quot; at Mumbai from 15th to 17th February 2017.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: transparent; resize: none; text-align: justify; position: relative; list-style: none;\">First prize for best oral presentation entitled &ldquo;Novel molecular mechanism producing weak D phenotype in Indians&rdquo; at 6th Annual conference of Indian society of transfusion medicine, 2017 held at Lucknow on 3-5th Nov, 2017.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: transparent; resize: none; text-align: justify; position: relative; list-style: none;\">Second prize for best oral presentation entitled Molecular mechanisms underlying Rhnull phenotype in India: First Report at Annual conference of Mumbai Haematology Group on 17-18th March, 2018.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: transparent; resize: none; text-align: justify; position: relative; list-style: none;\">My students abstract entitled &ldquo;Phenotypic characteristics of novel RhD variants in Indians&rdquo; was selected for Harold Gunson Fellowship by the Scientific Committee of the 28th Regional Congress of the International Society of Blood Transfusion 2017 (ISBT)</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: transparent; resize: none; text-align: justify; position: relative; list-style: none;\">Three weeks WHO sponsored Inter Regional workshop on &ldquo;External Quality Assessment For Transfusion Laboratory Practice Schemes&rdquo; at Regional National Thai Red Cross Society Bangkok , Thailand</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: transparent; resize: none; text-align: justify; position: relative; list-style: none;\">ICMR international fellowship for Senior Scientist (2012-2013) at Australian Red Cross Blood Service Trained for &ldquo;Non- invasive fetal RhD typing&rdquo; under Prof. Robert Flower, Research Programme Leader Queensland, Australia</li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; background: transparent; resize: none; text-align: ju